<h1 class="headline">5 Heartwarming Easter Stories During the Coronavirus</h1>
<div class="row">
<div class="col-xs-12">
<div class="contributor-img pull-left">
<a href="/author/katieyoder">
<img alt="Katie Yoder" class="img-thumbnail" src="https://media.townhall.com/townhall/reu/contributor-sm/authorimages/89523bba-047f-4fb7-9ee1-940ca81f54b9.png" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="contributor pull-left">
<a href="/author/katieyoder">Katie Yoder</a>
</div>
<div class="contributor pull-left">|</div>
<div class="contributor pull-left">Posted: Apr 12, 2020 12:01 AM</div>
